/small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>In progress The <code><strong>NavigatorOnLine</strong></code> interface contains methods and properties related to the connectivity status of the browser.</p>\n\n<p>There is no object of type <code>NavigatorOnLine</code>, but other interfaces, like <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> or <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, implement it.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The <code>NavigatorOnLine</code></em><em> interface doesn't inherit any property.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"navigatoronline.online_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/onLine\"><code>NavigatorOnLine.onLine</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indicating whether the browser is working online.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The </em><em><code>NavigatorOnLine</code></em><em> interface neither implements, nor inherit any method.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#navigatoronline\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-TW\">The definition of 'NavigatorOnLine' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>No change from the latest snapshot, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML5' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/#navigatoronline\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-TW\">The definition of 'NavigatorOnLine' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Snapshot of <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML Living Standard' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a> with its initial specification.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>on <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/29\" title=\"Released on 2014-04-29.\">29</a> (29)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>on <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>29.0 (29)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> interface that implements it.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/onLine\">Online and offline events</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"In progress The NavigatorOnLine interface contains methods and properties related to the connectivity status of the browser.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"NavigatorOnLine","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"NavigatorOnLine","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"